{"type": "article", "id": 40943, "title": "有了这种模块化眼罩，不用担心它合不合适的问题了｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-05-17T23:07:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 23101, "name": "52 Factory"}, {"id": 36795, "name": "Neon"}, {"id": 40575, "name": "Velco"}, {"id": 40576, "name": "Murray Fredericks"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 64, "image": "img/article/article_show/201705172113540evhngFILujY7RQW.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Manta Sleep Mask</h3><p>为了提高睡眠质量，很多人会选择戴上眼罩确保不被光线干扰。然而，由于每个人的脸型和睡姿都不相同，市面上现有的眼罩并不能做到百搭。为此，一个来自美国的设计团队历时一年多的时间研发了这款名为 Manta 的模块化眼罩。内置记忆海绵的眼罩部分可以根据用户的需要粘在指定的位置，贴合脸部的设计确保鼻梁处不会出现漏光的死角。尽管采用了全包覆的结构，由于眼罩中央预留了凹槽，佩戴时并不会压迫到眼睑。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/markzhang/manta-sleep-mask-upgrade-your-sleep-upgrade-your-l\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，售价从 20 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170517211442rDZ1MeUmPIsBKfoW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713235\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170517211441G50Nd1MQ82sWpPRB.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.507353\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170517211440yqSv3gwuXlcm8snF.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170517211442vwTz5cJdaO2VMkG7.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705172114434OLzprE16fVKgQda.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.119118\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170517211441vB7h0VqZdKSWIfA6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.829412\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Wink Bar by Velco</h3><p>想让自行车多点功能早就不再是什么难事了，但在法国自行车配件公司 <a href=\"http://velco.bike/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Velco</a> 看来，GPS 导航仪或是辅助照明设备很容易破坏车辆本身的外观，就像是添了补丁一样。为了让车主们更方便地为自行车升级，团队推出了这款名为 Wink Bar 的智能车把。它集成了照明、导航以及防盗功能：225 流明的前灯，会在处于黑暗状态时自动点亮；正前方的两块灯条则会根据用户在 app 中设定的目的地进行导航，还会在收到电话或是短信时发出提醒；如果自行车不幸被窃，用户可以通过 app 实时定位，它的追踪系统范围号称覆盖全球。除此之外，用户还能从 app 中查看骑行记录、和开车的花费对比、消耗的卡路里数等数据。这款车把目前正在 <a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/wink-bar-make-any-bike-smart-smartphone--2#/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Indiegogo</a> 上众筹，售价从 149 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170517211505MgdezlEhP6X4fK2L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170517211505RjAOtrBca18iy3U6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.534230\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170517211506pThLE9bskfRgrVN6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170517211506fu9k5SiTsmo7wZLO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170517211505HRz1EBT8DdeYrVaX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>RED DOLLS by 52 FACTORY</h3><p><a href=\"http://52factory.ru/\" rel=\"nofollow\">52 FACTORY</a> 是一个由来自俄罗斯圣彼得堡的 Nasya Kopteva 和 Sasha Braulov 共同创立的双人设计组合，擅长打造有故事背景的趣味小物。这套名为 RED DOLLS 的木制玩具是他们的最新作品，在造型上借鉴了俄罗斯传统玩具，黑白红三色构成的手绘图案则是从九位俄罗斯艺术家的作品中汲取的灵感，看起来就像是一个热闹的马戏团。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170517211539Sc8k5p2VD0OAm1qn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170517211538q0LnBxNHwuO7tZyJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170517211538aP7OVCBv264lwrT0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170517211539qnoAji1BNQIrR8tc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.041975\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170517211538lv0EkaKrbAqs2CQo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.535802\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Mirage Arabica Coffee by Karen Gevorgyan et al.</h3><p>你见过用风景插画来表现咖啡种类的包装吗？最近，来自亚美尼亚的几位学生就通过一幅描绘沙漠的水彩将五种咖啡联系在了一起，创造了这款名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/51516903/Mirage-Arabica-Coffee-Concept\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mirage</a> 的阿拉伯咖啡豆包装。画面中的每一个颜色代表了浓缩咖啡、牛奶、热水等原料，只要旋转咖啡盒最外层的盖子，人们就可以通过镂空的窗户感受到不同咖啡间的差异，充满了异域风情。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170517211523sxPwjvQhpcyAR0VX.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.534000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705172115236XVDpTx5N9voUAiE.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170517211523fjeG2LSpEkBszMb8.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170517211524tQx3yzYSChWdORmn.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170517211524PV2qZ9d3veY1Lfxw.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Pump House Pavilion by NEON</h3><p>作为伦敦旺兹沃思艺术节（<a href=\"http://www.wandsworthfringe.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Wandsworth Arts Fringe</a>）的一部分，<a href=\"http://pumphousegallery.org.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pump House</a> 画廊不久前委托了设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.seeneon.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">NEON</a> 与建筑公司 <a href=\"http://www.elliottwood.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Elliott Wood</a> 打造了一个由管材制作而成的临时凉亭。设计师参考了画廊入口处的经典的砖拱结构，将蓝色和黄色的软管交叉摆放后弯曲成一道道波纹状的拱形，远看仿佛有一种催眠的效果，吸引着人们步入凉亭一探究竟。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705172115501HO23uxwgecULNqY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.734719\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170517211551vTWXPZqpQbASGw8e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170517211551DtUeNOhvj41MsqYV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170517211551jOylg3WYc0LVMe7o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Vanity by Murray Fredericks</h3><p>自 2003 年起，澳大利亚摄影师 Murray Fredericks 多次携带着拍摄装备和生活用品，前往平整空旷的艾尔湖盐田（Lake Eyre），完成了一套名为 Vanity 的作品。在令人惊叹的风景中，Fredericks 特意抹去了人的存在，通过一方镜子吸引观众将注意力转移到周边的环境当中，去感受被定格的光线、色彩与空间。Fredericks 正在伦敦的 <a href=\"http://www.hamiltonsgallery.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hamiltons 画廊</a>举办自己的 <a href=\"http://www.hamiltonsgallery.com/exhibitions/113/works/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Salt:Vanity</a> 个人展，展览将持续至今年 6 月 14 日。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170517211656wJ4tjArcBdm1Oq07.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.774000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170517211656DEscf7JPkdieOWGl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.774000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170517211656Sn4eiNgzJ6vl0m2c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.774000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705172116574C9mHb2GcDEqRodL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.774000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705172116572PrfR5AIF6DVatmh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.774000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}